+------------+
|DEMENTIA DOS|
|MANUAL      |
+------------+

I. Command Interface
  KEYBOARD to type in command
  press - to run typed command
  press * to backspace command
  press + to run previous command

II. Basic Commands
  Clear the screen:    cls / clear
  print text:          echo
  leave Dementia Dos:  exit

III. File System Controls
    create a file:  cf
    read a file:    rf
    delete a file:  df

V.   Advanced Commands
  reprint the logo + clear the screen:  plogo
